ed="T" n="0786a23"/><persName key="A010689">釋師彥</persName>，姓<name>許</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000017104">閩越</placeName>人也。早悟羈縻，忽求<lb
ed="T" n="0786a24"/>拔俗，循乎戒檢，俄欲觀方。見<persName key="A008167">巖頭<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，領<lb
ed="T" n="0786a25"/>會無疑。初樂杜默<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1383"/>，似不能言者。後為所<lb
ed="T" n="0786a26"/>知敦喻，允請住<placeName key="PL000000014883"><placeName>台州</placeName><placeName>瑞巖山院</placeName></placeName>。時<persName key="A010691">道怤</persName>往參<lb
ed="T" n="0786a27"/>問，答對響捷，<persName key="A010691">怤<roleName>公</roleName></persName>神伏。後二眾同居，<persName key="A010689">彥</persName>之威<lb
ed="T" n="0786a28"/>德，凜若嚴霜。紏正僧尼，無容舛<anchor xml:id="beg0786sgsz4"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>悟</sic><corr>悮</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0786sgsz4"/>，故<placeName key="PL000000000197">江表</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0786a29"/>言御眾翦齊者，<placeName key="PL000000014883">瑞巖</placeName>為最。嘗有三僧，胡形<pb ed="T" n="0786b" xml:id="T50.2061.0786b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0786b01"/>清峭，目睛轉若流電焉，差肩並足致<anchor xml:id="beg0786003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>體</sic><corr>禮</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0786003"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0786b02"/><persName key="A010689">彥</persName>問曰：「子從何來？」曰：「<placeName key="PL000000048207">天竺</placeName>來。」「何時發？」曰：「朝行<lb
ed="T" n="0786b03"/>適至。」<persName key="A010689">彥</persName>曰：「得無勞乎？」曰：「為法忘勞。」乃諦視<lb
ed="T" n="0786b04"/>之，足皆不蹈地。<persName key="A010689">彥</persName>令入堂，上位安置，明旦<lb
ed="T" n="0786b05"/>忽焉不見，云是辟支迦果<ptr type="glossary" target="#g59"/>人，然莫知階級。<lb
ed="T" n="0786b06"/>時有不測人入法會，非止一過。<persName key="A010689">彥</persName>參學時<lb
ed="T" n="0786b07"/>號為<persName key="A010689">小彥長老</persName>。<placeName key="PL000000011455">兩浙</placeName><persName key="A003552">武肅王錢<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>累召，方肯<lb
ed="T" n="0786b08"/>來儀，終苦辭去。寺倉常滿。嘗有村媼來參<lb
ed="T" n="0786b09"/><anchor xml:id="beg0786sgsz5"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0786sgsz5"/>，<persName key="A010689">彥</persName>曰：「汝休拜跪，不如疾歸家，救取數十<lb
ed="T" n="0786b10"/>百物命，大有利益。」媼忩忙到舍，兒婦提竹<lb
ed="T" n="0786b11"/>器拾田螺正歸。媼接取，放諸水濆。又數家<lb
ed="T" n="0786b12"/>召齋，一一同日見<persName key="A010689">彥</persName>來食。至終<anchor xml:id="beg0786sgsz6"/>闍<anchor xml:id="end0786sgsz6"/>維，有巨<lb
ed="T" n="0786b13"/>蛇緣樹杪，投身火聚。當乎薪盡，舍利散飛，<lb
ed="T" n="0786b14"/>或風動，草木上紛紛而墜。神異絕繁，具如別<lb
ed="T" n="0786b15"/>錄。</p>
